Full length, on leg. Mahmudul Hasan Joy flicks it to mid-wicket.
Full length, on off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy gets it to backward point off the outer half.
Length ball, on the pads. Mahmudul Hasan Joy tucks it to the leg side.
Fuller, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy defends it to mid on off the inner half.
Short ball, just outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy leaves it alone.
Fuller, outside off, shaping away. Shadman Islam has no stroke to offer.
Length ball, around middle and leg. Shadman Islam blocks it back to the bowler.
Back of a length, outside off. Shadman Islam defends it to the off side.
On a length, outside off. Islam leaves it alone for the keeper. Some shape for Olivier this time.
Length ball, around off, hint of shape coming back into the left-hander. Shadman Islam plays it late and blocks it to cover.
Good length, on top of off. Shadman Islam remains solid in his defense.
Full length, at the off stumps. Mahmudul Hasan Joy defends it to the leg side off the inner half.
On a length, wide of off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy shoulders his arms at it.
Back of a length, outside off. Left alone.
Length ball, on top of off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy defends it solidly.
On a length, around off. Joy remains solid in his defense.
Length delivery, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy cuts it through covers for a single.
FOUR! Sheer timing from Joy! A bit too straight, full, around middle and leg. Mahmudul Hasan Joy stays back, closes the face of the bat and flicks it through the gap at mid-wicket for a boundary.
Full length, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy lunges and drives it to cover.
A sharp bouncer, on off. Joy ducks under it watchfully.
Length, on off. Joy blocks it out.
Full length, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy drives it through the cover region for a brace.
Back of a length, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy leaves it alone for the keeper.
Williams serves a short ball, around middle. Shadman Islam ducks underneath.
FOUR! Terrific shot! That made a cracking sound off the bat! Williams drops it short, around middle. Shadman Islam stands tall and pulls it well in front of square to bag a boundary.
Back of a length, around off. Shadman Islam keeps it out, off the back foot.
This is a full ball, outside off. Shadman Islam drives it through the cover region and collects a couple of runs.
A wayward ball, down leg. Shadman Islam gets inside the line of the delivery and lets it go through to the keeper.
Shorter in length, around off. Shadman Islam hangs back and blocks it solidly.
Olivier overpitches, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy drives it without much timing past the mid off fielder for a brace.
A length ball, angling in from off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy blocks it off the back foot.
Short of a length, just outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy gets behind the line and dead-bats it.
Good-length delivery, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy defends it off the front foot.
Olivier drops it short, yet again, this time it is outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy ducks underneath.
Pitches it up, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy prods and drives but finds the cover fielder.
Fuller in length, around off. Shadman Islam leans and drives it back to the bowler.
Williams dishes out a length ball, shaping away from outside off. Shadman Islam lets it through to the keeper.
Williams comes 'round the wicket and hurls a full-length ball, around off. Shadman Islam gets forward and blocks it to the off side.
On a length, around off. Shadman Islam gets behind the line of the ball and defends it.
Nicely played! A full ball, outside off. Shadman Islam leans and drives it through the cover region for a brace.
Short of a length, around off. Shadman Islam gets right on top of the bounce and dabs it onto the deck.
Tosses it up, outside off. Joy eases it to long on for a run.
Full and outside off. Shadman Islam pushes it to mid off.
An overpitched ball, around off. Shadman Islam leans and works it to the cover fielder.
Floated, full and around off. Shadman Islam gets forward and pushes it yet again towards mid off.
Tossed up delivery, around off. Shadman Islam blocks it solidly off the front foot.
This is full and around off. Shadman Islam clears his front leg and drives it back to the bowler.
Pitches it up, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy gets forward and works it behind square on the leg side for a single.
Crunched but straight to the fielder! Full and outside off. Shadman Islam drives hard but finds the mid off fielder.
Back of a length, angling away from outside off. Shadman Islam lets it be.
Williams bangs it into the deck, around leg. Shadman Islam ducks underneath.
A bit full, around middle and leg. Shadman Islam looks to defend off the front foot but it goes off the thick inside edge towards mid-wicket. The batters cross ends.
Nice and full, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy looks for a booming drive but it goes off the inner half of the blade to mid-wicket.
Tosses it up, around off. Shadman Islam clears his front leg and squeezes it out to cover.
Flatter ball, going on with the arm from off. Shadman Islam gets forward and blocks it.

OUT! TIMBER! Simon Harmer gets the breakthrough just at the stroke of Tea and Bangladesh lose their first wicket. This is a quicker ball, landing around off and going on with the angle. Shadman Islam stays back to block but he misses. The ball stays a touch low and sneaks through the gap between his bat and pad. It then crashes onto the stumps and the South Africans are delighted to see the back of Shadman Islam. THAT WILL BE TEA ON DAY 2!
Howout: b Simon Harmer

Commentary: Tossed up, around leg. Najmul Hossain Shanto prods and tucks it to square leg.
Tosses it up, on middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto keeps it out.
Fuller, on off, blocked back to the bowler. A wicket-taking over of Simon Harmer finally comes to an end.
Full, on middle. Joy pushes it back to the bowler.
Tossed up, full and on off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy prods and blocks it back to the bowler.

Mahmudul Hasan Joy steals a single this time. It is full, angled into the pads. Mahmudul Hasan Joy goes back and drives it to mid off. He takes on the arm of Dean Elgar and makes it safely to the other end.
Fuller, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto defends it back to the bowler.
Length, on off. Najmul Hossain Shanto tucks it to mid on.

FOUR! Najmul Hossain Shanto gets off the mark with a fantastic boundary. It is fuller, on off. Najmul Hossain Shanto drives it down the ground, it scoots past the effort of Dean Elgar's dive there and races away to the fence.
Floated, full and outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy prods to block it out.
Full, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy drives it on the up but straight to mid off.

FOUR! EDGY! Mahmudul Hasan Joy riding his luck at the moment. It is tossed up, full and outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy tries to drive it away. The ball takes the thick outside edge, goes past Keegan Petersen, at first slip and into the ropes at third man.
Great stop by the fielder! Fuller, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy guides it down to third man. The batters pick three before the fielder cuts it out.
Looped up, on off. Shanto defends it to point on the front foot.
Quicker, on the pads. Najmul Hossain Shanto flicks it to the leg side.
Loopy ball, on off. Joy defends it to the leg side.
Floated, full and angled into the pads. Joy tucks it to short leg.
Length ball, on off. Joy smothers it to cover.
Fuller, on leg. Joy clips it to square leg.
Short ball, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy stays back and cuts it to cover with the turn.
A maiden now from Keshav Maharaj. Full, on off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy defends it back to the bowler.
Loopy ball, outside off, turning away. Shanto does not chase it.
SIX! BANG! Down the ground! It is full, on leg. Najmul Hossain Shanto dances down the track and smokes it over the bowler's head for a biggie.
Tosses it up, on leg. Najmul Hossain Shanto blocks it on the front foot.
Fuller, at the stumps. Najmul Hossain Shanto gets his blade down in time to block it out.
Tossed up, on middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto prods and blocks it to short leg off the inner half.
Full, on off. Shanto pushes it to mid on and gets across for an easy single.
FOUR! Shanto greets Dean Elgar with a boundary. This is an overpitched ball, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto prods and carves it wide of the mid off fielder for a boundary.
Full and outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto carves it through the point region for a brace. 50 comes up for Bangladesh.
Tossed up delivery, around middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto drives it back to the bowler.
Floated, full and outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto works it wide of mid off and takes a run.
Flatter ball, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy drives it straight back to the bowler.
Looped up, on a length, well outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy eases it to long off and takes a single.
This is a flatter ball, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy keeps it out.
Floated, full and around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy defends it off the front foot.
Drags his length back, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy sits back and dabs it onto the deck.
Slightly short and outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy cuts it past the fielder at point for one run.
This is darted on the pads. Najmul Hossain Shanto rocks back and tickles it through fine leg for a run.
Tossed up delivery, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy gets forward and defends it.
Tossed up, on off. Najmul Hossain Shanto skips down the track and drills it back to the bowler.
Tosses it up, just outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto lunges forward and blocks it.
Floated, around leg. Najmul Hossain Shanto prods and tucks it around the corner for a brace.
Flatter and quicker, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto stays back and punches it to cover.
Flighted delivery, around off. Najmul Hossain Shanto dead-bats it.
A quicker ball, going on with the angle, from off. Najmul Hossain Shanto rocks back and defends it.

This is tossed up, around off and turning away late. Mahmudul Hasan Joy prods to defend but the ball beats his outside edge. Kyle Verreynne behind the sticks, collects the ball and disturns the stumps. He appeals and the leg umpire sends it upstairs. The replays though show that Joy has his back foot grounded.
Around off. Blocked out.
Flatter and quicker, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy keeps it out.
Looped up, on a length, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy defends it off the front foot.
Slower through the air, on off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy leans and blocks it solidly.
Angled down leg, Mahmudul Hasan Joy helps it round the corner for two runs.
Tosses it up, around off. Najmul Hossain Shanto defends it with ease.
Flatter and quicker, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto hangs back to cut but the ball stays a touch low and he misses.
On a length, around off. Najmul Hossain Shanto defends it to the off side.
This is floated, angling down leg. Najmul Hossain Shanto leans and glances it towards short fine leg.
Tossed up delivery, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto drives but the ball hits the silly point fielder.
Flatter ball, going on with the angle, from middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto looks to defend but it goes off the inner half of the blade towards mid-wicket for a run.
On off, blocked out solidly.
Full, outside off, it turns in sharply. Najmul Hossain Shanto defends it to the leg side.
Touch short, on off. Najmul Hossain Shanto flicks it through mid-wicket for a single.
Fuller, on middle and leg. Mahmudul Hasan Joy prods and defends it to the right of the bowler.
Quicker, on the pads. Mahmudul Hasan Joy flicks it to square leg for a single.
Short, on off. Najmul Hossain Shanto clips it through mid-wicket for one more.
Fuller, on middle and leg. Najmul Hossain Shanto defends it back to the bowler.
Full, on the stumps. Najmul Hossain Shanto defends it to mid-wicket off the inner half.
Short ball, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto was planning to come down the track, He stays back in the end and cuts it hard to point.

Flighted, full and on off. Najmul Hossain Shanto dances down the track and hits it hard back towards the bowler. Simon Harmer sticks hit right hand out and gathers the ball on a bounce. He dummies a throw at the batter, which forces Shanto to turn back and puts in a full stretched dive inside the crease to mark himself safe.
Quicker, full and on middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto gets an inside edge onto the pads.
Flighted, full and on off. Najmul Hossain Shanto waits for it and defends it out safely.
On off, defended out.
Fuller, on leg. Joy defends it to short leg.
Darted on the pads. Mahmudul Hasan Joy flicks it to mid-wicket.
Around off, defended out solidly.
Fuller, on off. Joy pushes it to mid off.
A full toss, on off. Joy hits it hard but only to mid on.
Looped up, full and on the stumps. Najmul Hossain Shanto blocks it out watchfully.
Flatter and on leg. Najmul Hossain Shanto goes back and blocks it out watchfully.
Quicker through the air, on leg. This one stays a touch low. Najmul Hossain Shanto gets his blade down in time to defend it out.
On off, blocked out solidly.
Full, on middle and leg. Najmul Hossain Shanto prods and defends it back to the bowler.
Full and quick, on leg. Shanto tucks it to mid-wicket.
It is looped up, around off. It grips and generates some bounce. Mahmudul Hasan Joy waits for it and deals with it easily.
On off, blocked back to the bowler.
Tossed up, on leg. Mahmudul Hasan Joy prods and smothers it out.
This is full, quicker and on the stumps. The ball stays low off the deck. Mahmudul Hasan Joy goes back and defends it out watchfully.
On off, eased back to the bowler.
Angled into the pads, Joy tucks it to short leg.
Flatter ball, around off. Najmul Hossain Shanto sits back and punches it back to the bowler.
That missed the off stump by a whisker! Tossed up, around off and turning away a tad. Najmul Hossain Shanto lets it be and the ball goes just past the off stump.
Around off. Blocked out.
Tossed up delivery, around off. Najmul Hossain Shanto defends it solidly.
An overpitched ball, around middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto eases it back past the bowler and takes a single.
Floated, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy blocks it with ease.
This is tossed up, around middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto eases it to long on for one run.
Flatter ball, on a length, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy taps it to the off side and the batters cross ends.
Full and around off. Najmul Hossain Shanto covers his off pole and works it to long off. Another single taken! Clever batting from these two!
Floated, around middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy keeps it out.
Slower through the air, full and on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy defends it off the front foot.
This is looped up, on a length, around middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy chips it to the mid-wicket fielder, on the bounce.
Floats it up, around off. Najmul Hossain Shanto keeps it out.
Full and outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto leans and works it to mid off.
Flatter and quicker, around middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto rocks back and defends it.
Nicely tossed up, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto lets it be.
Floated, full and around off. Najmul Hossain Shanto gets forward and defends it.
A quicker ball, full and on off. Najmul Hossain Shanto blocks it out.
Flatter and quicker, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy taps it to the off side and gets to the other end.
Tossed up, around off. Najmul Hossain Shanto keeps it out.
A mix-up but no harm done! Flatter ball, turning in from middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto rocks back and tucks it to mid-wicket. He wanted a single but is sent back by his partner.
Around off. Blocked out.
This is a full ball, outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto looks to sweep at first but he adjusts well in the end. He squeezes it out past the slip fielder for a brace.

An appeal for a run out and the decision has been sent upstairs. Tossed up, on middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto drills it back to the bowler. Keshav Maharaj sticks his left hand out but he fails to stop the ball and it goes onto hit the stumps at the bowler's end. The replays though suggest that Mahmudul Hasan Joy had his bat inside the crease before the ball hit the stumps.
Floated, full and outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy looks to drive but the ball spins in sharply and sneaks through the gap between his bat and pad.
Around off. Blocked out.
Floated, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy dead-bats it.
Joy runs down the track and keeps it out.
Nicely tossed up, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy prods and tucks it to mid-wicket.
This is a flatter ball, turning in from off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy hangs back and wrists it to mid-wicket. Maiden over from Simon Harmer!
Floated, full and outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto comes down the track and blocks it back to the bowler.
Full, on off. Shanto remains solid in his defense.
Full, angled into the pads. Shanto flicks it through square leg for a single.
Full, on middle and leg. Mahmudul Hasan Joy drives it back to the bowler.
Looped up, around off, it comes in with the arm. Mahmudul Hasan Joy goes back and taps it to the off side.
On middle and leg, Joy defends it out watchfully.
Floated, full and on off. Najmul Hossain Shanto eases it back to the bowler.
Looped up, full, just outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto dabs it to silly point.
Shorter, on off. Shanto taps it back to the bowler.
Full, outside off. Shanto blocks it out on the front foot.
Touch quicker, full and outside off. Shanto blocks it to short extra cover.
Flighted, angled into the pads. Shanto defends it back to the bowler.
Full, outside off, Joy drives it to cover.
Around middle Joy blocks it to short leg.
On off, blocked back to the bowler.
Full, on off. Joy eases it back to the bowler.
Around off, defended out solidly.
Tossed up, around leg. Mahmudul Hasan Joy flicks it to mid-wicket.
Tossed up, around off. Najmul Hossain Shanto keeps it out.
Floated, full and around off. Najmul Hossain Shanto blocks it off the front foot.
Looped up, around off. Najmul Hossain Shanto manages to defend it solidly.
Slower through the air, around middle. Najmul Hossain Shanto defends it with ease.
Edged but safe! This is tossed up, well outside off. Najmul Hossain Shanto throws his bat at it. It takes the thick outside edge and goes past the backward point fielder for a brace.
Flatter and quicker, around off. Najmul Hossain Shanto blocks it off the back foot.
Fuller, on off. Joy drives it back to the bowler with soft hands.
On off, Joy defends it on the front foot.
Three dots in a row now! Full and on leg. Joy clears his front leg and blocks it back to the bowler.
Fuller, on the pads. Joy defends it to short mid on.
Around middle and leg. Joy remains solid in his defense.
A maiden for Maharaj now. His fifth of the innings. Fuller, on the pads, Mahmudul Hasan Joy blocks it to short leg on a bounce.
SIX! BOOM! Tossed up, on off. Najmul Hossain Shanto skips down the track and smacks it over long off for a maximum. That also brings up the 50-run stand between these two!
Around off. Blocked out.
Tossed up, around off. Najmul Hossain Shanto keeps it out.
Floated, around off. Najmul Hossain Shanto blocks it off the front foot.
Floats it up, around off. Najmul Hossain Shanto dead-bats it.
Slower through the air, around off. Najmul Hossain Shanto defends it.
Around off, blocked out.
This is a flatter ball, going on with the arm, from middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy tucks it towards square leg.
Full and around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy defends it off the front foot.
Floated, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy wrists it to short leg.
Tossed up, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy gets solid in his front foot defence.
Flatter and quicker, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy cuts it past the point fielder for a brace.

OUT! TIMBER! WOW! That is a peach of a delivery from Simon Harmer to get rid of Najmul Hossain Shanto! An off-spinner's delight, to be precise. This one drifts in from middle, lands and then turns away from the batter. Najmul Hossain Shanto tries to defend it off the front foot but the ball goes past his outside edge and hits the top of the off pole. Shanto stands there in disbelief before he takes the long walk back to the pavilion.
Howout: b Simon Harmer

Commentary: Full and outside off. Mominul Haque pushes it to mid off.
Floated, around middle. Mominul Haque keeps it out.
An overpitched ball, around off. Mominul Haque dead-bats it.
This is a quicker ball that goes on with the arm, from off. Mominul Haque is a bit late to react. He looks to defend off the front foot but it hits the inner half of the bat and onto the deck.
In the air...but safe! Floated, full and around off. Mominul Haque looks to play it across the line but it takes the leading edge and falls in no man's land at the cover region.

A mix-up but no harm done in the end. Floated, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy taps it to point and looks for a run at first but then decides to go against it. Mominul Haque at the non-striker's end is halfway down the pitch. The throw comes towards his end but he misses his shy at the bowler's end and Mominul Haque escapes.
Nicely tossed up, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy keeps it out.
Looped up, on the pads, Mahmudul Hasan Joy flicks it to the leg side.
On the stumps. Joy defends it to the off side.
Fuller, on middle and leg. Joy prods and defends it to mid on.
Floated, full and on off. Joy defends it out watchfully.
Fuller, on leg. Haque defends it out with ease.
Touch short, on off. Haque blocks it to cover.

OUT! CAUGHT! Bangladesh lose their third wicket now. All thanks to Keegan Petersen under the helmet, who is placed at silly point. Simon Harmer is making the most of his comeback. He gets his third in no time. It is looped up, full, around off. Mominul Haque prods and tries to defend it out. He gets an inside edge onto the pads. The ball though lobs to the left of silly point. Keegan Petersen keeps his eyes on the ball, stretches his left arm out and the ball sticks in his palms. Keegan Petersen gets up and takes a victory lap, while the South African players chase him down to celebrate the wickets. South Africa well and truly on top in this game.
Howout: c Keegan Petersen b Simon Harmer

Commentary: Full and outside off. Mushfiqur Rahim prods and drives it through extra cover. He gets off the mark straightaway with a single.
In the air..but safe! Tossed up, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy chips it straight back to the bowler, on the bounce.

Aerial but it lands safely! Floated, full and around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy kneels and looks to slog-sweep but it goes off the top edge and lands just in front of the mid on fielder who backtracks to grab the ball. Two runs taken.
Around off. Blocked out.
Tosses it up, around off. Mushfiqur Rahim blocks it off the front foot.
Full and around off. Mushfiqur Rahim dead-bats it.
Full, on leg. Rahim flicks it to short leg.
Another one angled down leg. Rahim tucks it to the left of leg slip.
Fuller, on the pads, Rahim blocks it out easily.
Slower through the air, full and on off. Joy closes the face of the blade and blocks it to short leg.
Flatter, on the pads, Joy flicks it to square leg.
FOUR Nicely played. This should ease some pressure. Full length, wide outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy slashes it through covers for a boundary.
Full, on the stumps. Joy defends it into the deck on the front foot.
Fuller, on leg. Joy clips it to the right of mid on. The batters take a single before Ryan Rickelton blocks it out.
Looped up, angled into the pads. Mushfiqur Rahim clips it to the leg side.
Fuller, on the stumps. Mahmudul Hasan Joy flicks it to square leg.
Full and on the stumps. Joy defends it on the front foot.
On the stumps, blocked out solidly.
Angled into the leg stump. Joy remains solid in his defense.
Around off, defended out.
Darted on the pads. Mahmudul Hasan Joy tries to flick it away but works it back to the bowler off the leading edge. Luckily for him, it stays along the ground.
Floated, full and on leg. Rahim clips it to mid-wicket.
Full, on the pads. Rahim goes back and nudges it to the leg side.
Tossed up, on the pads. Mushfiqur Rahim flicks it to mid-wicket.

The umpire raises his finger for caught behind. Mushfiqur Rahim is not at all happy about the decision. He takes the review immediately. It is a loopy delivery, pitching around middle and turns down the leg side. Mushfiqur Rahim tries to flick it away. Kyle Verreynne takes a sharp catch to his left. The players appeal and the umpire thinks there is some blade on it and raises the dreaded finger. Mushfiqur Rahim takes the review and survives, as the UltraEdge confirms no bat is involved.
On off, blocked out.
Full, outside off. Rahim drives it to sweeper cover for two runs.
Fuller, angled into the pads. Joy clears his front leg and blocks it out.
Floated, full and on the stumps. Mahmudul Hasan Joy drives it through covers.
Fuller, on leg. Joy eases it back to the bowler.
Full, on the stumps. Joy lunges and blocks it out with ease.
Around leg, Joy defends it back to the bowler.
Full, on leg stump. Joy clips it to mid-wicket. This is the 128th ball that he faced.
Full, on leg. Rahim gets low and sweeps it to square leg. Unable to beat the fielder there.
Floated, full and on off. It grips and turns in a bit. Mushfiqur Rahim goes back and tucks it to short leg.
Short ball, outside off. Rahim punches it to cover.
FOUR! A much-needed boundary for Bangladesh. It is full and on leg. Mushfiqur Rahim gets low and sweeps it to deep square leg for a boundary.

A loud appeal for caught behind but turned down. Simon Harmer looked pretty sure that he got his man this time. He convinces his skipper to take it upstairs. It is a loopy delivery, angled down leg. Mushfiqur Rahim tries to flick it away but misses. It might've taken his gloves on the way. Dean Elgar goes for the review. The UltraEdge shows there is a spike as the ball passes the glove. The final decision is out and the on-field umpire is forced to change his decision. Simon Harmer is running havoc with the ball here, as he picks up his fourth wicket.
Howout: c Kyle Verreynne b Simon Harmer

Commentary: A dot to end this wicket-taking over by Simon Harmer. Floated, full and outside off. Ahmed pushes it to cover.
Short ball, outside off. Joy cuts it through point for a brace.
Fuller, on off. Joy prods and blocks it back to the bowler.
On off, blocked out.
Outside off, pushed to cover-point.
Fuller, on off, pushes it to cover.
Floated, full and on leg. Joy clips it past mid on for a single.
Tossed up, full and on the stumps. Joy clips it through mid on for a single.
Floated, full and outside off. Taskin Ahmed leans in and tries to defend it out. The ball grips and turns away. Although Ahmed gets beaten on the flight.
Full, on off. Ahmed blocks it on the front foot.
Fuller, on the stumps. Ahmed defends it to the right of the bowler.
Length ball, on off. Ahmed pushes it gently back towards the bowler.
Angled in full and on off. Ahmed blocks it out watchfully.
Length bal, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy eases it to mid off.
Full and on the stumps. Mahmudul Hasan Joy prods and blocks it out.
Full length, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy slashes it to cover off the inner half though.
Tossed up, full and on off. Joy blocks it to silly point.
Quicker, full and on off. Joy defends it to the leg side off the inner half.
Fuller, on leg. Joy blocks it out with ease. Keshav Maharaj gets his 10th maiden of the innings. THAT WILL BE STUMPS ON DAY 2.
Back of a length, angling down leg. Taskin Ahmed misses his nudge around the corner.
On a length, around off. Taskin gets forward and blocks it.
Williams drags his length back, around off. Taskin Ahmed taps it wide of the cover fielder for a single. Bangladesh are underway on Day 3!
No Ball! A short ball, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy ducks underneath. Williams oversteps and the umpire calls it no ball. 100 comes up for Bangladesh!
Good-length delivery, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy keeps it out watchfully.
Short of a length, just outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy gets on top of the bounce and defends it with soft hands.
Leg bye! A length ball, around leg. Joy misses his flick and gets hit just above his thigh pad. The ball rolls away for a leg bye.
A length ball, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy prods to block but it goes off the outer half of the blade towards cover-point.
A stifled appeal for LBW but that was going down leg. A full ball, nipping back in late from middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy misses his flicks and gets hit low on his pad.
Around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy gets forward and blocks it.
Good-length ball, just outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy defends it onto the deck.
This one comes in late from outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy looks to defend but it goes off the outer half of the bat towards backward point.
Play and a miss! Back of a length, well outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy sits back and looks to push it through the off side but he fails to get any bat on it. Olivier starts with a maiden over!

OUT! CAUGHT! Lizaad Williams gets his first wicket in Test cricket and he is delighted! Bangladesh's night watchman departs and this is a good start for South Africa! Back of a length, angling across the batter from outside off. Taskin Ahmed looks to push it through the off side, away from his body. He only manages a thick outside edge which goes straight to Wiaan Mulder at gully. Mulder looks to grab it with hard hands, the ball pops out of his hands, to his right and he recovers well to complete a juggling catch.
Howout: c Wiaan Mulder b Lizaad Williams

Commentary: On a length, around off. Liton Das keeps it out.
A length ball, outside off. Liton Das leaves it alone.
Shorter in length, angling in from outside off. Liton Das lets it be.

That nipped back in sharply! This delivery jags back in from off. Some extra bounce on offer for Williams. Liton Das sits back to block but he misses and gets hit high on his body. He seems to be in pain.
No ball! A full ball, outside off. Liton Das prods and pushes it to mid off. The umpire calls it a no ball as Williams oversteps.
Back of a length, outside off. Liton Das gets forward and defends it out.
A length ball, around leg. Mahmudul Hasan Joy tucks it behind square on the leg side and takes a single.
FOUR! Pulled away! A short ball, around off. Das stands tall and pulls it in front of square and gets off the mark in some style. A shot of authority from Das!
A wayward ball, well outside off. Das lets it through to the keeper.
FOUR! WHACKED! Das is making his intentions quite clear here! A length ball, outside off. Das hangs back and punches it through the cover-point region for a cracking boundary.
On a length, around off and shaping away late. Liton Das looks to defend but it goes off the outer half of the blade towards backward point.
This is a full ball, angling in from off. Das gets forward and pushes it to mid off, off the inner half of the bat.
Fuller in length, just outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy looks to drive without any feet movement. He gets an inside edge onto his pad.
Back of a length, angling in from middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy stays back and tickles it to fine leg for a single.
Shorter in length, around middle. Liton Das swivels and pulls it without much timing towards fine leg for a run.
A full ball, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy leans and drives it to the mid on fielder.
Another ball that is full and around middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy gets forward and works it to mid on.
Back of a length, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy gets behind the line of the delivery and blocks it solidly.
A length ball, jagging back in from outside off and staying a touch low. Das shoulders his arms to this one.
Good-length delivery, around off. Liton Das covers his off pole and keeps it out.
On a length, around off. Das blocks it to the off side.
Pitches it up this time, outside off. Das does not bother playing at it.
Fuller in length, around the fourth stump channel. Liton Das defends it off the front foot.
Good-length delivery, nipping back in slightly from outside off. Das lets it sail through to the keeper. Another maiden over from Olivier!
Lenght ball, outside off. Joy taps it to cover.
Full length, on off, blocked out.
Back of a length, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy sways away from the line of the delivery.
Length ball, on off. Joy defends it back to the bowler.
NO BALL! A sharp bouncer, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy leaves it alone. The umpire signals a no ball, as the bowler oversteps.
Back of a length, on the fourth stump line. It climbs onto the batter. Joy steers it straight to gully.
Bangs it short, around leg. Joy leaves it alone for the keeper.
Full length, on off, blocked out solidly.
Length ball, outside off. Das taps it to cover.
Fuller, on the off stump. Das blocks it back to the bowler.

FOUR! Edgy! A short ball, on the bodyline. Liton Das swivels and heaves across the line. The ball flies off the top-edge, beats the diving effort of Kyle Verreynne behind the sticks and races over the ropes at fine leg.
On a length, outside off. Das punches it through covers for a brace.
Length, on the pads. Liton Das clips it through mid-wicket for a single.

EDGED AND DROPPED! A regulation catch at slips and it is the skipper, Dean Elgar who fails to pouch it. A length ball, outside off, shaping away a touch. Liton Das goes fishing away from his body. The ball takes the thick outside edge and goes towards first slip. Dean Elgar though misses out on a dolly.
Full length, on off. Das blocks it back to the bowler.
Length ball, on the pads. Das clips it to mid-wicket. The fielder does well to not let it race away.
Length, on off, blocked to cover.
Full length, on fourth stump. Liton Das pushes it gently back to the bowler.
Fuller, on the pads. Das clips it to mid-wicket.
Full, on off, Joy eases it to mid on.
Fuller, on the pads, Joy flicks it to mid-wicket.
Tossed up, full, on middle and leg. Mahmudul Hasan Joy defends it to the leg side off the inner half.
Floated, full and on off. Joy defends it solidly on the front foot.
Darted on the pads, Joy nudges it to square leg for a single this time.
Fuller, on off. Das lunges and blocks it forward.

FOUR! Mahmudul Hasan Joy welcomes Harmer into the attack in a fine manner. Tossed up, full and outside off. Joy slaps it down the ground and bags a boundary at long off. He gets to his second Test fifty. The pavilion rises to applause this knock.
Floated, full and on off. Joy flicks it towards mid on. Dean Elgar misfields and the batters take a brace.
On off, pushed back to the bowler.
Looped up, around off, defended out.
Touch short, on the pads. Joy pulls it to square leg.
Full, on middle and leg. Mahmudul Hasan Joy prods and defends it to the right of the bowler.
Tossed up, around off. Liton Das keeps it out.
Floated, full and around middle. Liton Das gets forward and blocks it.
Flatter and quicker, full, around off. Liton Das dead-bats it.
Tossed up delivery, around off. Liton Das blocks it.
Slower through the air, on a length, around middle. Liton Das hangs back and dabs it onto the deck.
In the air...but safe! Flighted delivery, full and on off. Das looks to play it across the line. It goes off the leading edge, just past the short cover fielder. A maiden from Keshav Maharaj!
FOUR! BANG! Tossed up, in the slot, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy clears his front leg and whacks it past the diving fielder at mid on for a boundary.
Around off. Blocked out.
Tossed up, on off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy drives it back to the bowler.
Harmer comes over the wicket now. He serves it on a length, around middle and turning in late. Mahmudul Hasan Joy stays back and tucks it to square leg.

SIX! BOOM! This is some batting from Mahmudul Hasan Joy! Good intent shown by the tourists on Day 3! This is tossed up, on middle. Joy skips down the track and lofts it way over long on for a maximum.
Around off. Blocked out.
Nicely tossed up, around off. Liton Das gets forward and keeps it out.
Floated, full and on off. Liton Das defends it off the front foot.
A loopy ball, around off. Liton Das leans and defends it towards the silly point fielder.
FOUR! Nicely done! Flatter ball, on a length, around off. Liton Das hangs back and just guides it through the third man region for a boundary. Runs have suddenly started to flow for Bangladesh!
Tosses it up, outside off. Liton Das prods and defends it towards the point region. The batters cross ends.
Floats it up, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy keeps it out.
Tossed up, outside off. Liton Das gets forward and wrists it to mid-wicket.
This is darted on the pads. Liton Das works it past the short leg fielder for a run.
Tosses it up, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy skips down the track and eases it to long on for a single.

FOUR! Nicely timed! Slightly shorter in length, flatter and around middle. Das rocks back and just whips it through the mid-wicket region. The ball races away to the fence. Excellent timing on that one!
Floated, on middle. Liton Das looks to heave it across the line but it goes off the inner half of the blade towards square leg for a run.
Top delivery! Harmer tosses it up, around off and turning in sharply. Mahmudul Hasan Joy looks to defend but he gets an inside edge onto his pad.
Full and outside off. Liton Das drives it wide of the long off fielder for a single.
Nicely tossed up, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy keeps it out.
This is flatter and quicker, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy rocks back and works it to the backward point fielder.
Floated, on a length, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy lunges forward and blocks it.
A loopy ball, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy stretches forward and defends.
Slower through the air, full and around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy gets to the pitch of the ball and blocks it.
Fuller, on the pads. Das clips it to square leg for a single.
Full, on the stumps. Joy comes down the track and hits it back to the bowler.
Fuller, on leg. Joy defends it to short leg.
Looped up, outside off, it grips and turns in. Mahmudul Hasan Joy defends it solidly.

DROPPED! A tough chance though. It is fuller, on middle and leg. Mahmudul Hasan Joy presses forward and tries to defend it out. The ball takes the outside edge and goes to the right of short leg. The fielders initial movement was to his left which takes him away from the ball.
On off, blocked out solidly.

What a peach of a delivery. The South African players look excited. They take the review for caught behind. It is a flighted delivery, on off. The ball grips and turns away. Liton Das presses forward, tries to defend it out but misses. The ball zips past the outside edge. Keshav Maharaj puts in a loud appeal but the umpire is unmoved. The UltraEdge confirms no bat is involved. Although the sound that the players must've heard, was of Das' bat hitting his boot.
LEG BYE! Tossed up, on the pads. Das fails to flick it. The ball goes to square leg off the pads. The batters cross for a leg bye.
Fuller, on off. Joy blocks it back to the bowler.

Loopy ball, full and on off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy gets low and goes for the sweep. It flies off the top edge and goes over square leg. Lizaad Williams runs backward but is unable to reach in time. The batters take a single.
On off, blocked out.
Fuller, on off. Das remains solid in his defense.
Quicker, fuller and down leg. Mahmudul Hasan Joy goes back and takes a blow on his pad. Down the leg side though.
Full, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy pushes it to mid off.
TWO LEG BYES! Loopy ball, around off. It grips and turns away down the leg side. The batters collect two leg byes, as it races down to fine leg off the pads.
On off, defended out solidly.
Fuller, on middle, turning down leg. Joy clips it to the leg side.
Full, outside off, Joy defends on his front foot.
Full, on middle and leg. Das blocks it to short leg.
BEATEN! Floated, full and outside off. It grips and turns away a touch. Liton Das presses forward but fails to block it out. Gets beaten on the outside edge.
Fuller, on middle, blocked back to the bowler.
Angled into the pads, Das tucks it to short leg.
Fuller, on leg. Das clips it to short leg on a bounce.
Floated, full and around off. It grips and turns away sharply. It beats Das all ends up, as he tries to defend on the front foot.
Outside off, blocked back to the bowler.
Full, on off, Joy defends it out watchfully.
Full length, wide outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy drives it through covers for a brace.
Tossed up, on the pads. Joy clips it to mid-wicket for an easy single.
Fuller, on middle and leg. Liton Das smothers it to short leg.

Simon Harmer strikes on Day 3! But the celebration has to wait as Liton Das takes the review for caught behind. He challenges the umpire's decision here. It is loopy ball, angled down leg. Liton Das tries to flick it away but might've got the thinnest of inside edge. Simon Harmer appeals and the umpire raises his dreaded finger. Liton Das takes no time to opt for the review. The UltraEdge shows no bat is involved. It confirms that the ball comes off the thigh pad instead. The on-field decision has to be overturned. Thw bowlers need to toil harder to break this stand.
Around off, blocked out.
Floated, full and around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy keeps it out.
On middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy tucks it to the leg side for a single.
Inside edge saves Liton Das this time! Tossed up delivery, around off. Liton Das prods to block but it goes off the inside edge and onto the pads.
Around middle. Liton Das clips it to mid-wicket for a single.
Floated, on off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy blocks it.
Das skips down the track and works it to mid-wicket.
Flighted delivery, around middle. Liton Das gets forward and keeps it out.
Slightly short and around off. Liton Das rocks back and dabs it onto the deck.
This is darted on the pads. Liton Das hangs back and tucks it around the corner.
Nicely tossed up, around middle. Liton Das flicks it towards square leg.
Tossed up delivery, around off. Liton Das defends it off the front foot.
Turn and bounce! Floated, on a length, around off and turning away sharply. Mahmudul Hasan Joy gets squared up as he tries to defend it. It goes off the outside edge past the slip fielder for a run.
Around off. Blocked out.
Tossed up, on off. Liton Das defends it off the front foot.
Cut away! Flatter and quicker, outside off. Liton Das hangs back and cuts it past the point fielder. The batters take three runs.
Floated, on a length, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy leaves it alone.
A loopy ball, full and around middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy plunges forward and blocks it.
Flatter ball, on a length, around off. Liton Das hangs back and tucks it around the corner for a run.
An overpitched ball, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy skips down the track and pushes it back to the bowler.
On a length, around middle. Joy defends it.
Tosses it up, around middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy lunges forward and dead-bats it.
Slightly short and around middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy gets low, rocks back and pulls it towards the square leg fielder.
This lands on a length, outside off and turns in late. Mahmudul Hasan Joy gets an inside edge onto his pad as he looks to keep it out.
On a length, around middle. Liton Das blocks it with ease towards mid-wicket and takes a run.
Full and around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy defends it solidly.
FOUR! Short and outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy sits back in his crease and cuts it behind square on the off side for a boundary. Top shot. He picked the length so early!
Floated, on a length, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy blocks it off the front foot.

FOUR! WHACKED! Another ball that is short and outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy rocks back and slashes hard through the cover region for another boundary. This is now the highest score by a Bangladeshi opening batter against South Africa in Tests.
Around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy blocks it.
This is darted on the pads. Liton Das misses his nudge on the leg side and gets hit on his pad.
FOUR! Good use of the feet! Tossed up, around middle. Liton Das skips down the track and whacks it through the mid-wicket region for a boundary.
Nicely tossed up, on off. Liton Das blocks it.
DROPPED! A length ball, around leg. Liton Das tickles it straight to the leg slip fielder. Wiaan Mulder there gets low to his left but puts it down.
On a length, around off. Liton Das defends it off the front foot.

An appeal for caught at short leg but the umpire says no! South Africa have opted for a review! This is tossed up, around off and turning in sharply. Das prods to block but he misses and gets hit on his pad. The ball lobs up towards the short leg fielder who grabs it and South Africa appeal. The umpire is unmoved. The UltraEdge shows that there was clear daylight when the ball passed the bat. The on-field decision remains. The Proteas lose a review.
Angled into the pads, blocked to short leg.
Fuller, on leg. Joy goes back and pushes it back to the bowler.
Quicker and fuller, on the stumps. Joy goes deep inside his crease and blocks it out.
Nicely tossed up, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy blocks it out.
Flatter and quicker, outside off. Joy rocks back and cuts it past the point fielder for a single.
Floated, around off. Liton Das blocks it off the front foot.
Full and around middle. Das drags it to long on for a run. Joy moves to 80. This is now the highest score by a Bangladeshi player against South Africa in Test cricket.
Around off, blocked out.
Flatter and quicker, turning in from middle. Liton Das tucks it to square leg.
Floated, full and outside off. Das dead-bats it.
On a length, around middle and leg. Liton Das glances it through fine leg and rotates the strike.
Nicely tossed up, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy leans and dabs it onto the deck.
Flatter and quicker, around off. Liton Das pushes it back to the bowler, off the back foot.
Floated, full and around off. Liton Das keeps it out.
Slower through the air, on a length, around middle. Liton Das sits back and wrists it to mid-wicket.
Tossed up delivery, around off. Liton Das defends it off the front foot.
TURN AND BOUNCE! This one drifts in from off and then turns away sharply. Liton Das looks to defend at first but does well to sway away from the line of the ball in the end.
This is darted on the pads. Liton Das clips it behind square on the leg side for a single. THAT WILL BE LUNCH ON DAY 3!
Back of a length, outside off. Liton Das leaves it alone.

OUT! BOWLED! Straight through the gate! That is a pearler from Lizaad Williams to get his second wicket of the innings! He strikes straightaway after Lunch break and this is a much-needed breakthrough for South Africa. Good-length delivery, jagging back in from the fifth stump channel. Das stays back to block but he misses. The ball brushes off his pad and cannons onto the stumps. Just the kind of start South Africa would have wished for after the break.
Howout: b Lizaad Williams

Commentary: On a length, around middle. Yasir Ali keeps it out.
Back of a length, outside off. Yasir Ali shoulders his arms to this one.
A short ball, angling down leg. Yasir Ali ducks underneath.
Pitches it up, just outside off. Yasir Ali prods and defends it solidly.
Full length, wide outside off, it moves away off the deck. Mahmudul Hasan Joy slashes at it but misses.
Full length, yet again, wider than the previous delivery. Kyle Verreynne has to move a long way to his right to gather the ball. No shot offered.
Full length, on the pads. Joy flicks it through square leg for a single.
Fuller, on the pads. Ali clips it to deep square leg for a brace. He gets off the mark.
The new ball is angled full and into the pads. Ali clears his front leg and tucks it to mid-wicket. Unable to thread it through the gap this time.
Full length, on off. Ali punches it to mid on with soft hands.
Full length, on the stumps. Joy stays back, closes the face and tucks it to mid-wicket for a quick single. He moves to 82.
Fuller, angled down leg. Ali flicks it to deep square leg for one more.
Back of a length, outside off. Joy guides it through backward point for two more runs.
Shorter again, outside off. Joy cuts it straight to point.

FOUR! Powerful stroke! Mahmudul Hasan Joy is on a roll. Lizaad Williams continues to bowl short, wide outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy rides the bounce really well and cuts it through point for a boundary.
Fuller, on the off stump. Joy gets his blade down just in time to defend it back to the bowler.
A sharp bouncer, on off. Ali sways away from the line of the delivery and leaves it alone.
Full length, on fifth stump. Ali defends it to cover on the front foot.
On a length, outside off, shaping away. Ali shoulders his arms at it.
Fuller, on off. Ali blocks it back to the bowler.
Length ball, on the pads. Ali clips it to deep square leg for one.
Back of a length, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy defends it to point.
Short ball, on top of off. Yasir Ali hangs back and blocks it to point.
Fuller, angled into off. Ali tucks it to short mid on.
A slower bouncer, down leg. Ali leaves it alone for the keeper.
Back of a length, outside off. Ali gets on top of it and cuts it hard through backward point. The batters take two before the fielder cuts it out.
Full length, outside off. Yasir Ali lunges and shoulders his arms at it.
Fuller, on the pads. Ali clips it to deep square leg for one.
Full length, outside off. Ali defends it out to cover.
Full length, on the pads, Ali flicks it to deep mid-wicket. The batters take two runs. 200 comes up for Bangladesh!
A length ball, in the corridor of uncertainty. Ali tries to defend inside the line but gets beaten, as the ball zips past the outside edge.
Good length, wide outside off. Ali leaves it alone.
Touch short, outside off. It nips in off the deck. Yasir Ali gets cramped for room here, but does enough to block it out.
A length ball, outside off. Ali looks to chase it but misses.
Back of a length, around leg. Mahmudul Hasan Joy tickles it to fine leg for a single.
On a length and outside off. Yasir Ali lets it through to the keeper.
A length ball, jagging back in from off. Yasir Ali gets forward and defends it towards mid on.
Short of a length, around off. Yasir Ali keeps it out, off the back foot.
On a length, around off. Yasir Ali hangs back and blocks it.
On a length, around middle and leg. Yasir Ali tucks it past the mid-wicket fielder and takes a run.
Edged but safe! Good-length ball, just outside off. Yasir Ali prods and looks to defend with soft hands. It takes the outside edge and runs past the gully fielder for a couple of runs.
Olivier strays on the pads. Yasir Ali clips it towards the fine leg fielder for a run.
Short of a length, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy keeps it out watchfully.
Back of a length, well outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy defends it to the off side.
Play and a miss! A short ball, well outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy throws his bat at it but he fails to make any connection.
This is full and around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy blocks it out.
A full ball, outside off. Yasir Ali drives it back to the bowler.
FOUR! Top shot! Fuller in length, outside off. Yasir Ali drives it through the mid off region and bags a boundary. Excellent timing on that one!
FOUR! Back-to-back boundaries! Short and wide, outside off. Yasir Ali cuts it through the point region and collects a boundary.
A full ball, outside off. Yasir Ali pushes it towards cover.

A length ball, around middle and leg. Yasir Ali tucks it around the corner and sets off for a run. Temba Bavuma at square leg, fails to grab the ball cleanly and Mahmudul Hasan Joy makes it safely to the striker's end.

Another ball, full and outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy drives hard through cover. Dean Elgar there, puts in a dive and stops a certain boundary. The batters take a run. Mahmudul Hasan Joy moves into the 90s.

OUT! RUN OUT! Oh, dear! This is the last thing that Bangladesh would have wanted at this stage! A huge mix-up in the middle and it is Yasir Ali who has to walk back to the hut. This was a length ball, around leg. Mahmudul Hasan Joy tucks it towards deep mid-wicket and gets to the other end. Yasir Ali though looks to sneak in another run. Mahmudul Hasan Joy is not interested and he doesn't go for it. Ryan Rickelton in the deep throws it to the keeper. Kyle Verreynne collects the ball by moving forward and whips the bails off by running towards the stumps. Both the batters are left stranded at the non-striker's end. Bangladesh lose their seventh wicket now.
Howout: run out (Ryan Rickelton / Kyle Verreynne)

Commentary: Good-length ball, around leg. Mehidy Hasan tucks it to the leg side for a run.
On a length, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy lets it be.
Short of a length, well outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy does not bother playing at that one.
On a length, shaping away from outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy lets it through to the keeper.
A length ball, shaping in from outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy shoulders his arms to this one.
Tossed up, on off. Mehidy Hasan keeps it out.
BEATEN! A flatter ball, landing just outside off and going on with the arm. Mehidy Hasan looks to block but the ball zips past his outside edge.
Floated, on a length, around off. Hasan dead-bats it.
Tosses it up, around middle. Hasan blocks it off the front foot.
Edged but safe! Flighted delivery, outside off. Mehidy Hasan covers his off pole and looks to block. It takes the outside edge and goes past the slip fielder for a single.
Flatter and quicker, around middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy gets back in his crease and dabs it onto the deck.
Back of a length, on off. Mehidy Hasan hops inside the crease and blocks it out to cover.
A length ball, on top of off. Hasan blocks it back to the bowler with full face.
Short ball, angled down the leg side. Mehidy Hasan leaves it alone for the keeper.
Outside off, left alone by Hasan.
Back of a length, outside off. Mehidy Hasan dabs it to point.
On a length, outside off. Hasan punches it to point.
Fuller, on off. Joy dances down the track and pushes it back to the bowler.
FOUR! EDGY! It is tossed up, wide outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy throws the blade at it. The ball races away to the third man fence off the outside edge. He moves to 95.
Fuller, on the pads, Joy goes back and tucks it to the leg side.
Fuller, on middle and leg. Joy clips it to mid-wicket.
Angled into the pads. Joy tucks it to short leg.
Joy does see off this over really well. It is full, on middle and leg. Joy leans forward and clips it square on the leg side.
Looped up, on the pads. Hasan tucks it to the leg side.
Fuller, on off, Hasan blocks it out watchfully.
Full, on off. Hasan prods and blocks it to silly point.
Looped up, full and on off. Hasan pushes it to cover for a quick single.
Tosses it up, on off. Joy prods and blocks it back to the bowler.
Full and on off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy remains solid in his defense.
Fuller, on off. Hasan blocks it to the right of the bowler.
Wide outside off. Hasan pushes it to cover on the front foot. They take one.
Tosses it up, on the stumps. Mahmudul Hasan Joy defends it back to the bowler.
Full, on middle and leg. Joy defends it to short leg off the inner half.
Full, on off, defended out watchfully.
Quicker, full, on the pads. Joy flicks it to square leg.
Full, on the stumps. Hasan prods and blocks it out.
Full, on off. Hasan blocks it in front of him.
On off, defended to cover.
Tossed up, on off. Hasan defends it watchfully.
Around off, defended to cover.
Full, on off. Hasan defends it to off side.
A quicker ball, on middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy tucks it to mid-wicket and takes a quick single.
Nicely tossed up, around off. Mehidy Hasan keeps it out.
Flatter and quicker, around off. Mehidy Hasan rocks back and dead-bats it.
Floated, on a length, around middle, from 'round the wicket. Mehidy Hasan gets forward and blocks it.
SIX! Mehidy Hasan breaks the shackles! This is tossed up, around middle. Hasan kneels and slog-sweeps it over the deep mid-wicket region for a maximum. Excellent shot!
Tossed up, around off. Mehidy Hasan defends it out.
Nicely tossed up, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy blocks it off the front foot.
Tossed up, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy plants his front foot forward and dabs it onto the deck.
Around off, blocked out.

A direct hit at the bowler's end but Mahmudul Hasan Joy makes it home. This is tossed up, around off. Joy pushes it to mid off and takes a single. A direct hit at the non-striker's end and the ball ricochets off the stumps towards the leg side. The batters steal another run. Joy moves to 98.

HUNDRED FOR JOY! What a fine, fine knock this has been from the Bangladeshi opener! He becomes the first Bangladesh player to score a century against South Africa in Test cricket. This is a flatter ball, outside off. Joy cuts it through the point region and comes back for the second run. He removes his helmet, raises his bat towards the dressing room. His teammates are ecstatic and they give a round of applause to what has been a terrific knock from the youngster. Joy though would be looking to bat deep and take his team to a much better position from hereon.
On the pads, Joy flicks it to square leg.
Fuller, on the stumps. Hasan tucks it to the left of short leg.
On the pads, Hasan goes back and blocks it to the leg side.
Flatter, on middle. Hasan remains solid in his defense.
Darted on the pads, Hasan clips it to the leg side.
Full and on off, Hasan lunges and defends it forward.
On off, Hasan defends it back to the bowler.
Just short of the short leg fielder! Tossed up, on middle. Joy looks to block it with hard hands. It hits the splice of his bat and lands just in front of Sarel Erwee at short leg.
Nicely tossed up, around off. Blocked out.
A full ball, around middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy clears his front leg and whips it towards square leg.
Floated, full and around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy keeps it out watchfully.
Flighted delivery, around off. Joy defends it off the front foot.
Floated, full and around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy dead-bats it. Back-to-back maiden overs for South Africa!
Back of a length, around off. Mehidy Hasan gets on top of the bounce and blocks it.
Shorter in length, around off. Mehidy Hasan defends it solidly.
On a length and well outside off. Mehidy Hasan lets it be.
Back of a length, outside off. Mehidy Hasan lets it sail through to the keeper.
Good-length delivery, around off. Mehidy Hasan keeps it out.
This is darted on the pads. Mehidy Hasan tucks it around the corner and rotates the strike.
This is full and down leg. Mehidy Hasan gets down on his knee and sweeps it straight to the short fine leg fielder.
FOUR! Easy pickings! A flatter ball, around leg. Hasan gets forward and just tickles it through the fine leg region for a boundary.
Bye! A full ball, down leg. Mehidy Hasan misses his sweep and the keeper fails to grab the ball cleanly. The batters cross for a bye.
Nicely tossed up, on off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy keeps it out.
Around off. Blocked out.

Edged but safe! Floated, full and around middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy looks to defend off the front foot. The ball spins away, takes the outside edge and goes past the first slip fielder for a couple of runs.
FOUR! Top shot! Back of a length, outside off. Mehidy Hasan cuts it over point and bags a boundary.
FOUR! Back-to-back boundaries. The stand moves to 35. A short ball, outside off yet again. Mehidy Hasan slashes hard at it. It goes past gully and into the third man fence.
Full, on the pads, Hasan clips it to square leg for a single.
Full length, on off, Joy defends it out solidly.
Length ball, on off. Joy defends it to the off side.
On a length, outside off. Joy leaves it alone for the keeper.
On off, defended out solidly.
Fuller, on middle and leg. Hasan blocks it back to the bowler.
Flighted, onto the pads. Hasan defends it out by pressing forward.
Around leg. Hasan clips it to short leg.
Floated, full and on the pads. Hasan tucks it to short leg yet again.
Short and outside off. Hasan pucnhes it to cover.
Outside off. Joy pushes it to mid off.
Full length, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy drives it gently to mid off.
Fuller, on the stumps. Joy smothers it back to the bowler.
The dots continue to creep up. This time it is sharp bouncer, on off. Joy ducks under it watchfully.
Length ball, outside off. Joy dabs it to point.
Full length, on middle and leg. Joy eases it to mid on.
Full and on the stumps. Mehidy Hasan blocks it out with full face.
Tossed up, full and outside off. Hasan leans in and defends it to the off side.
Loopy ball, around middle and leg. Hasan prods to block it out.
Flatter, outside off. Hasan blocks it out watchfully.
Just evades the short leg fielder. It is quicker, on the pads. Hasan goes back to defend it out. He gets an inside edge onto the pads. The ball goes to the right of the short leg fielder.
On off, blocked out.
Full and on off. Joy defends it into the deck.
Fuller, outside off. Joy drives it to wide of long off for a brace.
Fuller, on the pads. Joy blocks it to short leg.
Tossed up, around middle and leg. Joy defends it to short leg off the inner half.
Full, on the pads. Mahmudul Hasan Joy flicks it over mid-wicket for two runs.
NO BALL! Fuller, on off. Joy blocks it back to the bowler. The umpire signals a no ball as the bowler oversteps.
On off, defended out.
Fuller, on off. Hasan lunges and blocks it to silly point.
Full, on the pads, Hasan clips it to short leg.
On off, Hasan defends it forward on the front foot.
Angled into the pads, Hasan tucks it to short leg.
Five dots on the trot now! Floated, full and on leg. Hasan remains solid in his defense.
Fuller, outside off. Mehidy Hasan steps forward and drives it to mid off. THAT WILL BE TEA ON DAY 3.

Mulder starts with a full ball, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy reaches out and slices it towards the gully fielder, on the bounce. A stifled appeal for catch and the umpires have sent it upstairs. The replays clearly suggest that it was a bump ball.
A full ball, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy drives it to the mid off fielder.
Fuller in length, angling in from middle. Mahmudul Hasan Joy leans and works it to mid on.
No Ball! On a length and outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy leaves it alone. The umpire calls it no ball as the bowler oversteps.
Fuller in length, just outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy keeps it out, off the front foot.
Uppish but safe! A length ball, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy chips it just past the cover fielder and collects a couple of runs.
On a length, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy defends it with ease.
Flatter ball, outside off. Mehidy Hasan stays back to cut but he misses.
Flatter ball, on a length and turning in from off. Mehidy Hasan gets right back to defend it.
An overpitched ball, on middle. Mehidy Hasan squeezes it out to mid on.
Floated, on a length, around middle. Mehidy Hasan blocks it.
Flighted delivery, around off. Mehidy Hasan drives it through the cover region for a single.

Is that dropped? Tossed up, around off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy looks to block off the front foot. He gets a thick outside edge towards Keegan Petersen who is a bit late to react. He gets fingertips to it but fails to grab it cleanly.
Good-length ball, around off. Mehidy Hasan defends it towards point.
On a length and angling in from middle. Mehidy Hasan blocks it off the back foot.
This is on a length, around middle. Mehidy Hasan gets right behind the line of the ball to defend.
Pitches it up, around off. Hasan gets solid in his defence.
Fuller in length, around off. Mehidy Hasan keeps it out.
A yorker-length ball, around off. Mehidy Hasan digs it out watchfully. A maiden over from Wiaan Mulder!
Flatter and quicker, outside off. Joy guides it to third man for a brace.
Angled into the pads. Joy tucks it to the leg side.
Fuller, outside off. Joy drives it to the right of mid off. The fielder there moves to that side and makes an excellent stop.
On off, Joy prods and blocks it back to the bowler.
Tossed up, full and on leg. Joy defends it out watchfully.
Full, on middle and leg. Mahmudul Hasan Joy stays back and clips it to short leg.
Full length, angled into off. Hasan defends it to cover.
FOUR! Mehidy Hasan stepping on the gas here. It is full and outside off. Mehidy Hasan leans in and creams it through covers for a boundary.
Good length, outside off, it nips away sharply off the deck. Mehidy Hasan does not go fishing away from his body.
OH DEAR! Mehidy Hasan is fortunate this time. Back of a length, on off. Hasan tries to pull his bat back but is a tad late to do so. The ball bumps into the deck and sneaks past the stumps.

OUT! CAUGHT AT SLIPS! Wiaan Mulder strikes and breaks a crucial stand for his side. It is an outswinging delivery, full and outside off. Mehidy Hasan goes for the expansive drive but does not middle it. In fact, the ball takes the outside edge and flies straight into the palms of Simon Harmer at first slip who makes no mistake. Although, there was a slight halt in celebration as the umpire wanted to check the front foot. The replays suggest that it is a legal delivery. Can South Africa end things quickly for Bangladesh?
Howout: c Simon Harmer b Wiaan Mulder

Commentary: Full length, on the pads. Ahmed clips it to the leg side.
Fuller, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy reverse-hits it to cover.
SIX! BANG! Mahmudul Hasan Joy talking with his blade now. This is full and outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy kneels and slogs it over the mid-wicket fence for a biggie.
Full, on the stumps. Joy defends it back to the bowler.
FOUR! Short and punished! Mahmudul Hasan Joy is on a roll. It is short, around middle and leg. Mahmudul Hasan Joy makes some room, latches onto it and cuts it hard through covers for a boundary.
On off, blocked back to the bowler.
Really good batting by Joy! It is short and outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy steers it to short third man for a single. Joy to retain the strike.
A length ball, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy tries to punch it to the off side. The ball takes the under edge and goes towards the keeper.
FOUR! Mahmudul Hasan Joy has only one job now. He is certainly taking the attack to South Africa now. Full length, on off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy gets under it and lofts it over mid off for a boundary.
FOUR! Back-to-back boundaries. Mahmudul Hasan Joy is displaying great skills. Full length, wide outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy strides and lifts it over mid off for another boundary.
FOUR! Three on the trot! It is a short ball, on off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy pulls it to deep mid-wicket for a boundary.
Full length, on middle and leg. Joy tucks it to short mid-wicket. He could not get the single he was looking for.

FOUR! Mahmudul Hasan Joy ends the over by bagging the fourth boundary. It is a short ball, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy waits for it and guides it smartly through the slip cordon for four. The deficit now goes down to 73.
Full length, angled down leg. Khaled Ahmed fails to flick it off his pads. He gets pinged, Duanne Olivier appeals but the umpire is unmoved.
Full length, on off. Khaled Ahmed flicks it to mid on.
A yorker length delivery, on middle and leg. Khaled Ahmed digs it out solidly.
A sharp bouncer, on off. Khaled Ahmed leans back and leaves it alone for the keeper.
Duanne Olivier bends his back and serves a short ball, on off. Khaled Ahmed tries to sway away from the line but takes a blow on his body.

Short ball, on off. Khaled Ahmed tries to defend it out but it looks like he pulls his blade back in time. Duanne Olivier and company appeal for caught behind. The keeper is really excited after the take. The umpire though does not raise his finger. South Africa take a review for caught behind. The UltraEdge confirms that there is a spike as the ball passes the glove. The on-field decision is forced to be overturned. Khaled Ahmed walks back to the pavilion.
Howout: c Kyle Verreynne b Duanne Olivier

Commentary: Full length, on the stumps. Mahmudul Hasan Joy defends it to the leg side.
Fuller, on middle and leg. Mahmudul Hasan Joy flicks it to deep square leg but does not run to the other end.
A yorker, angled into off. Joy digs it out watchfully.

FOUR BYES! Free runs for Bangladesh. A length ball, outside off. It stays low off the deck. Mahmudul Hasan Joy slashes hard but it sneaks under his blade. The ball goes through the keeper for a boundary. The umpire signals byes.

OUT! CAUGHT! A valiant knock of Joy comes to an end. Lizaad Williams picks up his third wicket of the innings. It is a short ball, outside off. Mahmudul Hasan Joy throws his blade at it. The ball takes the outside edge and goes towards the man at first slip. Simon Harmer takes a stunning catch. BANGLADESH GET BUNDLED OUT AT 298.
Howout: c Simon Harmer b Lizaad Williams

Commentary: BEAUTY! Good-length delivery, around off and shaping away late. Erwee pokes at it but the ball zips past his outside edge.
On a length, around off. Sarel Erwee keeps it out.
Back of a length, around off. Sarel Erwee hangs back to defend this one.
A length ball, jagging away from outside off. Sarel Erwee dabs it onto the deck.
Back of a length, around leg. Sarel Erwee tucks it around the corner and takes a run. Erwee and South Africa are up and running!
A length ball, nipping back in from well outside off. Elgar lets it be.
Nicely tossed up, around off. Sarel Erwee pushes it back to the bowler.
Flatter and outside off. Sarel Erwee rocks back and punches it to the cover fielder.
A quicker ball, going on with the arm from middle. Sarel Erwee stays back and tucks it to mid-wicket.
Floated, full and outside off. Erwee prods and defends it to point.
An arm ball that goes on with the angle, from off. Sarel Erwee keeps it out.
Turn and bounce! Floated, full and outside off. Sarel Erwee looks to drive away from his body. He misses as the ball rips past his outside edge. Mehidy Hasan starts with a maiden over!

An appeal for caught behind but the umpire is not interested! Bangladesh have opted for a review though! This is tossed up, well outside off. Dean Elgar reaches out and looks to drive but the ball spins past his outside edge. The keeper collects the ball and they appeal. The umpire says no and Bangladesh take it upstairs. The UltraEdge rolls in and it shows that there was no deflection when the ball passed the bat. The on-field decision stands.
Around middle. Dean Elgar tucks it to the leg side for a run.
On a length, outside off. Sarel Erwee pushes it to cover.
Shorter in length, outside off. Sarel Erwee punches it through cover and rotates the strike.
Flatter and quicker, outside off. Dean Elgar works it through the off side and collects a single.
BEATEN! Floated, full and outside off. Sarel Erwee looks to defend but the ball spins past his outside edge.
Flatter and quicker, around off. Dean Elgar rocks back to defend it.
Floated, around off. Dean Elgar prods to keep it out.
On a length, outside off. Dean Elgar leans but lets the ball go through to the keeper.
Slightly shorter in length, outside off. Dean Elgar cuts it to the backward point fielder. The fielder there half-stops it and the batters take a single.
On a length, around off. Sarel Erwee dead-bats it.

Ouch! That might have hurt! An overthrow and they get the single in the end. This was tossed up, around off. Sarel Erwee pushes it to cover. The fielder there, collects the ball and has a shy at the striker's end. However, the ball hits Yasir Ali at silly point who tries to duck under it. Ali gets hit on his helmet and the ball ricochets past the keeper. The batters steal a single.
On a length, and outside off. Sarel Erwee leaves it alone.
Good-length delivery, around off. He blocks it off the front foot.
On a length, and way outside off. Left alone.
Full and outside off. Erwee leaves it alone.
A length ball, angling across the batter. Sarel Erwee does not bother playing at it.
On a length, around leg. Erwee tucks it around the corner for a brace.
Nicely tossed up, around off. Dean Elgar prods and keeps it out.
FOUR! This is sliding down leg. Dean Elgar gets forward and just tickles it through the fine leg region for a boundary.

An appeal for LBW but the umpire is not interested! Bangladesh have opted for a review. Umpire's call on wickets hitting and Dean Elgar survives! Tossed up, on middle and turning away late. Elgar prods to defend but the ball spins past his blade and hits his back pad. The UltraEdge rolls in and it shows that the ball would have clipped the off stump. Bangladesh do not lose their review this time. Also, it is four byes as the ball rolls away to the third man fence.
On a length, around off. Dean Elgar keeps it out.
Shorter in length, outside off. Dean Elgar cuts it through covers for a run.
Tosses it up, around off. Sarel Erwee keeps it out.
Good-length ball, angling across the batter from outside off. Dean Elgar lets it be.
BEATEN! A length ball, just outside off and shaping away from the batter. Dean Elgar feels for it but the ball rips past his outside edge.
Fuller in length, around off. Dean Elgar pushes it back past the bowler for a couple of runs.
Back of a length, outside off. Dean Elgar hangs back and pushes it to cover.
Shorter in length, angling across the batter, from just outside off. Dean Elgar lets it through to the keeper.
Fuller and wider, outside off. Dean Elgar shoulders his arms at it.
Nicely tossed up, around off. Sarel Erwee keeps it out.
Flatter and quicker, around off. Sarel Erwee covers the line and dabs it onto the deck.
Floated, full and outside off. Sarel Erwee stretches forward and defends.
Tossed up delivery, outside off. Sarel Erwee leaves it alone.
A quicker ball, full and outside off. Sarel Erwee lets it be.
Full and around off. Sarel Erwee pushes it back to the bowler. A maiden over!
Back of a length, outside off. Dean Elgar does not bother playing at it.
Short of a length, well outside off. Dean Elgar lets it sail through to the keeper.
Chopped on, almost! On a length and shaping away from off. Dean Elgar looks to push it through cover but it goes off the thick inside edge just past the leg stump.
Full and outside off. Dean Elgar sits back and lets it be.
Back of a length, around middle. Dean Elgar dabs it onto the deck.
FOUR! SMASHED! Good-length delivery, around off. Dean Elgar hangs back and caresses it through the cover region for a boundary.
Tossed up, on off. Sarel Erwee keeps it out.
Full and around off. Sarel Erwee defends it off the front foot.
Flatter and quicker, around off. Sarel Erwee blocks it out watchfully.
An arm ball, going on with the angle, outside off. Sarel Erwee stays back and punches it to the cover fielder.
Play and a miss! Hasan serves a loopy ball, well outside off. Sarel Erwee reaches out and looks to slap it through the cover region. The ball goes past his outside edge.
Floated, on a length, around off. Erwee defends it off the front foot. A maiden over from Hasan!
Back of a length, outside off. Elgar taps it to backward point.
Full length, on the pads, Elgar tucks it to short mid-wicket.
Length ball, on off. Blocked out.
EDGED BUT SHORT! A full-length ball, on off. Dean Elgar tries to work it to the leg side. The ball takes the outside edge and lands short of the man at first slip.
Length ball, on off. Elgar defends it out watchfully.
FOUR! Top shot! Much better from Elgar. Full length, angled into the pads. Dean Elgar waits for it and places it to perfection past mid on for a boundary.
Floated, full and around off. Sarel Erwee leans in and tries to defend it out but misses. The ball zips past the outside edge.
Short, outside off. Sarel Erwee cuts it to cover.
On the pads, Sarel Erwee flicks it to square leg for a single.
Fuller, outside off, turning away. Elgar lets it be.
Tossed up, full and outside off. Elgar taps it to point for a quick single.
Fuller, on the pads. Sarel Erwee clips it to mid-wicket.
Back of a length, outside off. Dean Elgar shoulders his arms at it.

FOUR! Dean Elgar bags another boundary in the morning session. Too straight, on the pads. Dean Elgar flicks it to fine leg for a boundary. The lead is into the three figures now. It is 102 to be precise.
Touch short, on off. Dean Elgar hops and clips it to mid-wicket. Dean Elgar ventures out looking for a single, but Sarel Erwee does well to deny it.

Full length, on off. Dean Elgar blocks it back to the bowler. Ebadot Hossain throws the ball down the leg side. Liton Das, behind the sticks, had to work extremely hard to stop the ball. Ebadot Hossain is clearly frustrated and he has a chat with Elgar before the umpire intervenes.
A length ball, on the pads. Elgar clips it to square leg for a single.
LEG BYE! Length ball, on the pads, Sarel Erwee fails to flick it away. He gets pinged on his pads. Ebadot Hossain makes a stifled appeal but the umpire shows no interest. They cross for a leg bye.
Fuller, on the fourth stump. Sarel Erwee drives it to covers for an easy single.
Full, on off. Dean Elgar defends it to point.
Looped up, on off. Dean Elgar stays back and blocks it out watchfully.
Floated, full and outside off. It stays low a tad as it turns away. Dean Elgar cuts it to cover.
On middle and leg, tucked to short leg.
LEG BYE! Angled down the leg side. Elgar fails to pick it up. The ball brushes the pads and rolls towards fine leg. The batters take a leg bye.
Full length, angled in on off. Dean Elgar walks forward and blocks it back to the bowler.
Length, on off, defended out.
Full length, outside off. Dean Elgar defends it to cover on the front foot for a single.
Length, on the pads. Sarel Erwee clips it to square leg for a single.
Length ball, outside off. Dean Elgar defends it to mid off.
A single to end the over! Length ball, outside off. Dean Elgar works it to point for a single.
A low full toss, around leg. Elgar flicks it through the square leg region for a brace. A rare loose delivery from Mehidy Hasan!
Flatter ball, on a length, outside off. Dean Elgar prods and leaves it alone.

An appeal for LBW but the umpire is unmoved! Hasan goes wide of the crease and serves a quicker ball, on a length, just outside off. Dean Elgar prods and pads it away. Bangladesh do not opt for a review.
Floated, on a length, outside off and spinning away late. Dean Elgar gets forward to defend but the ball zips past his outside edge.
Flatter and quicker, outside off. Dean Elgar cuts it through the cover regio for a couple of runs.
This is an arm ball, around middle and going on with the angle. Dean Elgar tucks it wide of the mid-wicket fielder for a couple of runs.

A loud shout for LBW but the umpire shakes his head! Hossain comes 'round the wicket and hurls a full ball, angling in from middle. Erwee looks to flick it behind square on the leg side but he misses and gets hit on his pad. The replays suggest that the ball would have surely gone down leg.
Around off. Blocked out.
Short of a length, outside off. Erwee shoulders his arms at it.
Fuller in length, outside off. Sarel Erwee lets it be.
On a length and way outside off. Sarel Erwee lets it through to the keeper.

Inside edge saves Erwee this time! Back of a length, nipping back in from outside off. Erwee looks to defend but he gets an inside edge onto his thigh pad. Hossain yet again exchanges some words with the batter. Excellent bowling from Ebadot! A maiden!
Tossed up, around off. Elgar keeps it out.
Full and around middle. Elgar works it to mid-wicket.
This is a quicker ball, on a length, around middle. Elgar stays back and tucks it to square leg with soft hands.
Tosses it up, well outside off. Dean Elgar leaves it alone watchfully.
Hasan comes over the wicket now and serves a flatter ball, around leg. Elgar tickles it through fine leg for a couple of runs.
Tossed up, outside off. Dean Elgar looks to sweep but he misses.
A short ball, outside off. Erwee cuts it to the point fielder.
Back of a length, around middle. Sarel Erwee tucks it to mid-wicket.

An appeal for LBW but turned down! Bangladesh opt for a review! Three reds on the Ball Tracker and Erwee is a goner!
